OL,7,FWhat is cyberflashing and epilepsy-
OL,8,Ftrolling?
OL,10,FCyberflashing is the sending of
OL,11,Funwanted sexual images, whilst
OL,12,Fepilepsy-trolling involves abusers
OL,13,Fsending flashing images electronically
OL,14,Fwith the intention of harming people
OL,15,Fwith epilepsy.
OL,17,FOther offences listed as part of the
OL,18,Fact include sending death threats, the
OL,19,Fsharing of revenge porn and sending
OL,20,Ffake news that aims to cause
OL,21,Fsubstantial harm.
