OL,7,FTechnology Secretary Michelle Donelan
OL,8,Fsaid: "From today, online abusers and
OL,9,Ftrolls will be prosecuted and put
OL,10,Fbehind bars for their cowardly and
OL,11,Fmenacing acts - ensuring the public
OL,12,Fare protected and can have better
OL,13,Fpeace of mind when online.
OL,15,F"Our pioneering Online Safety Act is
OL,16,Falready setting a global standard, and
OL,17,Fpivotal protections like these will
OL,18,Fkeep sick individuals off our streets
OL,19,Fand unable to endanger Brits online."
OL,21,FWhat punishment could people face?
