OL,7,FWhile sending death threats or
OL,8,Fthreatening serious harm online will
OL,9,Fcarry a prison sentence of up to five
OL,10,Fyears, under a new threatening
OL,11,Fcommunications offence.
OL,13,FAnd a new false communications offence
OL,14,Fwill outlaw the intentional sending of
OL,15,Ffalse information designed to cause
OL,16,F"non-trivial psychological" or
OL,17,Fphysical harm to users online.
