OL,7,FSiobhan Blake, from the CPS, said:
OL,8,F"Women and girls should be able to go
OL,9,Fabout their lives and daily commutes
OL,10,Fwithout being subjected to and
OL,11,Fbombarded with unwanted sexual images.
OL,13,F"Our prosecutors are ready and
OL,14,Fcommitted to tackling this
OL,15,Funacceptable behaviour.
OL,17,F"We would encourage anyone who has
OL,18,Fbeen subjected to the illegal act of
OL,19,Fcyberflashing to come forward and
OL,20,Freport it.
